55 void MoveGroupSequenceService::initialize()
56 {
57  command_list_manager_ = std::make_unique<pilz_industrial_motion_planner::CommandListManager>(
58  ros::NodeHandle("~"), context_->planning_scene_monitor_->getRobotModel());
59 
60  sequence_service_ = root_node_handle_.advertiseService(SEQUENCE_SERVICE_NAME, &MoveGroupSequenceService::plan, this);
61 }

63 bool MoveGroupSequenceService::plan(moveit_msgs::GetMotionSequence::Request& req,
64  moveit_msgs::GetMotionSequence::Response& res)
65 {
66  // Handle empty requests
67  if (req.request.items.empty())
68  {
69  ROS_WARN("Received empty request. That's ok but maybe not what you intended.");
70  res.response.error_code.val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::SUCCESS;
71  return true;
72  }
73 
74  // TODO: Do we lock on the correct scene? Does the lock belong to the scene
75  // used for planning?
76  planning_scene_monitor::LockedPlanningSceneRO ps(context_->planning_scene_monitor_);
77 
78  ros::Time planning_start = ros::Time::now();
79  RobotTrajCont traj_vec;
80  try
81  {
82  // Select planning_pipeline to handle request
83  // All motions in the SequenceRequest need to use the same planning pipeline (but can use different planners)
84  const planning_pipeline::PlanningPipelinePtr planning_pipeline =
85  resolvePlanningPipeline(req.request.items[0].req.pipeline_id);
86  if (!planning_pipeline)
87  {
88  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Could not load planning pipeline " << req.request.items[0].req.pipeline_id);
89  res.response.error_code.val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::FAILURE;
90  return false;
91  }
92 
93  traj_vec = command_list_manager_->solve(ps, planning_pipeline, req.request);
94  }
95  catch (const MoveItErrorCodeException& ex)
96  {
97  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Planner threw an exception (error code: " << ex.getErrorCode() << "): " << ex.what());
98  res.response.error_code.val = ex.getErrorCode();
99  return true;
100  }
101  // LCOV_EXCL_START // Keep moveit up even if lower parts throw
102  catch (const std::exception& ex)
103  {
104  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Planner threw an exception: " << ex.what());
105  // If 'FALSE' then no response will be sent to the caller.
106  return false;
107  }
108  // LCOV_EXCL_STOP
109 
110  res.response.planned_trajectories.resize(traj_vec.size());
111  for (RobotTrajCont::size_type i = 0; i < traj_vec.size(); ++i)
112  {
113  move_group::MoveGroupCapability::convertToMsg(traj_vec.at(i), res.response.sequence_start,
114  res.response.planned_trajectories.at(i));
115  }
116  res.response.error_code.val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::SUCCESS;
117  res.response.planning_time = (ros::Time::now() - planning_start).toSec();
118  return true;
119 }
